1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:05,220 --> 00:00:07,339
Ten thousand taels, non negotiable.

4
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:08,779
Installments accepted.

5
00:00:08,780 --> 00:00:10,139
Thirty percent down payment,

6
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:11,660
with monthly interest of one percent.

7
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:15,339
Suisui.

8
00:00:15,340 --> 00:00:17,060
I'll agree on Father's behalf.

9
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:19,500
Not a tael less than ten thousand.

10
00:00:20,740 --> 00:00:22,740
Now that's being sensible.

11
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:26,339
This is the deposit.

12
00:00:26,340 --> 00:00:28,180
I'll pay back the rest slowly.

13
00:00:28,260 --> 00:00:29,659
Good stuff.

14
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:30,739
Worth two hundred taels.

15
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:33,739
That leaves nine thousand
eight hundred taels.

16
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:35,180
I'll write you a promissory note.

17
00:00:49,820 --> 00:00:50,779
Deal.

18
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:52,340
Payment made, goods delivered.

19
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:53,779
Uncle,

20
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,539
next time you want to hurt someone,
remember to bring enough money.

21
00:00:57,540 --> 00:00:58,660
You...

22
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:02,460
Rui'er!

23
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:04,300
You traitor!

24
00:01:14,140 --> 00:01:16,099
Father, what's wrong?

25
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:17,420
Father!

26
00:01:18,340 --> 00:01:21,460
He's fine. He's just mad.

27
00:01:21,740 --> 00:01:22,999
He'll be better after some sleep.

28
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,899
Father, let's go.
Let's head to the military camp.

29
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,499
The soldiers are still hungry.

30
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:30,260
Mm.

31
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,700
Greetings, Your Highness.

32
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,059
Your Highness.

33
00:01:39,060 --> 00:01:39,779
Little Princess.

34
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:40,860
You're here.

35
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:50,100
I can't go on anymore.

36
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:55,020
I don't have any strength left.

37
00:01:56,740 --> 00:01:58,019
These aren't rice grains at all.

38
00:01:58,020 --> 00:01:59,139
They're all husks.

39
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:00,100
Exactly.

40
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,380
They swapped the grain

41
00:02:02,540 --> 00:02:04,260
and then burned the granary.

42
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:06,460
So it really wasn't a natural disaster.

43
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:07,939
That's awful.

44
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:10,419
How dare they toy with the lives

45
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,700
of the soldiers?

46
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:14,339
I'm going to use
the rewards Grandfather gave me

47
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:16,299
to buy food for the soldiers.

48
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,500
I bought grain!

49
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:21,900
Soldiers!

50
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:25,060
Your Highness!

51
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,379
Your Highness,

52
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:27,980
you're here!

53
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:31,060
It's all my fault for being useless.

54
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:33,940
I spent the whole day
running around outside.

55
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:37,939
I searched all over Jiacheng Pass,

56
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:39,060
but

57
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:42,259
not a single granary or grain supplier

58
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:44,140
was willing to sell me any grain.

59
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:52,260
In the end, I found a private seller

60
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:56,660
and bought this tiny bit at a high price
from scattered households.

61
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:58,060
If there's really no other way,

62
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:01,860
I'll cook this rice into
a few pots of porridge

63
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,380
and distribute it to

64
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:05,620
the soldiers first.

65
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:09,500
This little?
How can it possibly be enough?

66
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:25,420
There's food.

67
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:29,100
We're saved!

68
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:31,420
Wonderful!

69
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,339
We're finally saved!

70
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:34,780
Now we finally have food to eat!

71
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:42,020
Wow, that's so much!

72
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,980
Ah, wonderful!

73
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,900
We're saved!

74
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:50,739
Father, I told you.

75
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:52,979
As long as I'm here,
everyone will be fine.

76
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:53,659
That's right.

77
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:57,419
Suisui is my little lucky star.

78
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,020
Wonderful!

79
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,460
(What's going on?)

80
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:03,380
(Why does it feel so cold?)

81
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:16,379
Eat more.

82
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:17,219
Get nice and plump,

83
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:19,339
then carry me around later.

84
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:20,659
You're eating grass,

85
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:21,660
yet dreaming big.

86
00:04:21,860 --> 00:04:23,980
You're not Ning Huchen,
the King of Zhenbei.

87
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:26,459
The horses in his family
all get premium rice.

88
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,619
I'm so jealous.

89
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:30,939
No grain shops
are selling grain right now,

90
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:31,819
so how are his horses

91
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:33,260
eating premium rice?

92
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:35,459
See? You don't know this.

93
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:37,119
All the grain shops around Jiacheng Pass

94
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,980
belong to Ning Huchen and his wife.

95
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,459
Forget premium rice.

96
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:42,740
They can even get tribute grain.

97
00:04:43,780 --> 00:04:45,379
Exactly.

98
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:47,539
The Ning family's horses
just got new golden saddles again!

99
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,939
Same horse, different fate.

100
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,539
When will I

101
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,139
ever get to live like that?

102
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:53,740
If all the grain shops belong to him,

103
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,840
that means

104
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:59,379
the key to the grain supply
lies with him.

105
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:00,499
Young Mistress.

106
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,739
I know about the Ning family.

107
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:03,459
Ning Huchen fears nothing,

108
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:04,459
except his wife.

109
00:05:04,460 --> 00:05:06,939
After all, everything
he has today came from her.

110
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,259
He's completely whipped.

111
00:05:08,260 --> 00:05:09,939
But unfortunately...

112
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:11,380
Unfortunately what?

113
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:13,139
His wife

114
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:14,699
has been trying for a child for years.

115
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:17,699
She's been praying at temples everywhere,
hired Taoists to perform rituals,

116
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:19,099
and tried every folk remedy possible,

117
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,360
but still couldn't get pregnant.

118
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,320
Ning Huchen is so worried
he's practically gone gray.

119
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:23,459
Blessings like that

120
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:25,099
can't be forced before their time.

121
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:25,899
(Blessings...)

122
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:28,139
(This is exactly what I'm best at.)

123
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:30,740
(I'm the lucky star herself.)

124
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:33,020
Father, I thought of a way!

125
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:44,039
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

126
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:47,879
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

127
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:51,399
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

128
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:54,360
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

129
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:58,879
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

130
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:02,640
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

131
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:06,039
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

132
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:10,080
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

133
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:19,359
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

134
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:22,999
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

135
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:26,719
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

136
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:30,359
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

137
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:34,039
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

138
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,959
♪Endlessly flowing♪

139
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:42,160
♪Good fortune♪
